@startuml class_cqrs_ddd
!theme plain

title CQRS / DDD Models

class CommandModel {
    + Name : string
    + Properties : List<PropertyModel>
}

class QueryModel {
    + Name : string
    + Properties : List<PropertyModel>
}

class RequestHandlerModel {
    + RequestType : string
    + ResponseType : string
    + EntityName : string
}

class ResponseModel {
    + Name : string
    + Properties : List<PropertyModel>
}

class RequestValidatorModel {
    + Name : string
    + RequestType : string
}

class EntityModel {
    + Name : string
    + Properties : List<PropertyModel>
}

class AggregateModel {
    + Name : string
    + Properties : List<PropertyModel>
    + Commands : List<CommandModel>
    + Queries : List<QueryModel>
}

class DbContextModel {
    + Name : string
    + Entities : List<string>
}

class DbContextInterfaceModel {
    + Name : string
    + Entities : List<string>
}

note as N1
  CommandModel and QueryModel implement
  MediatR IRequest<T> pattern.
  RequestHandlerModel implements
  IRequestHandler<TRequest, TResponse>.
end note

AggregateModel *-- "0..*" CommandModel : Commands
AggregateModel *-- "0..*" QueryModel : Queries
AggregateModel o-- EntityModel : root entity

CommandModel .. RequestHandlerModel : handled by >
QueryModel .. RequestHandlerModel : handled by >
RequestHandlerModel .. ResponseModel : returns >
CommandModel .. RequestValidatorModel : validated by >

DbContextModel *-- "1..*" EntityModel : DbSet<T>
DbContextInterfaceModel .. DbContextModel : interface for >

@enduml
